title: Husky Liners X-act Contour Series | Front Floor Liners - Black | 55251 | Fits 2020-2022 Hyundai Palisade 2 Pcs
features: TOUGH NEVER FELT SO SOFT — Rubberized DuraGrip construction yields the perfect balance of strength & pliability, not that hard “plastic” feel of lesser liners.

PERFECT EDGE-TO-EDGE FIT — Floorboards are 3D laser-scanned using our proprietary FormFit design process, for an ultra-tight, glove-like fit for your make & model. Built to stay flat to the edge, no curls no gaps.
LIFE CONTAINED, NOT STAINED — Its patented FormFit Edge creates a raised barrier along the door jam that keeps mud, snow, and liquids contained for easy clean up.
TAKE IT OUT, HOSE IT DOWN, CARRY ON — X-act Contour is flexible and easy to remove and clean up; spray it down, shake it off, and it’s back on the job. Proudly made in the USA, warrantied for life.
description: Survival of the fittest starts with the best fit. Husky X-act Contour liners combine laserscanned, exact fit with a no-slip, DuraGrip surface and a softer feel. It’s the highest evolution of the same grit-tough durability that’s gone into the Husky brand since 1988. Built for abuse that would curl the edges of lesser liners. It locks to your vehicle’s factory retention posts, with the added stability of our Stay-Put Nibs for a no-slip, no-slide, surface with absolutely zero compromise in protection. They’re made to stand up to whatever you’re laying down— including chemicals like battery acid and oil, with our FormFit Edge to keep spills contained for easy cleanup. Just remove, spray, and they’re back on the job. Available in black. Built to last a lifetime, warrantied the same. Right here in Winfield, Kansas, America.
